OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCouples 'devastated' by    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffamily visa rule changes   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Couples planning a new life in the UK  
OL,6, have been left heartbroken by changes  
OL,7, restricting who can apply to live here.
OL,9,FFrom April 2024, British citizens or   
OL,10,Fpeople already settled in the UK will  
OL,11,Fneed to show they earn #38,700 before  
OL,12,Ftheir overseas partner can live here   
OL,13,Fwith them - a sharp jump from the      
OL,14,Fcurrent threshold of #18,600.          
OL,16,FThey also still need to show they are  
OL,17,Fin a marriage or civil partnership when
OL,18,Fthey apply for a family visa, intend to
OL,19,Fbe within six months, or that they have
OL,20,Fbeen living together for at least two  
OL,21,Fyears.                                 
